FreeSurfer files for FSAVG.

Use tpl-fsaverage_den-164k_hemi-*_sphere.surf.gii in wb_command for the
surface-based transformations.

For registration using surftracc (CIVET tools), any sphere can be used
(since the .sm map is vertex based and not coordinate bases) so spheres
using CIVET's inflate_to_sphere_implicit were used. Note: Use the same
inflation tool on both surfaces for registration to ensure similar
projections on the sphere.
